<span id="freeTextContainer15577030147256547277">The fact that I got this as an omnibus means a lot. If these were presented to me in single book form, I would not have read them. They would have automatically be deemed too short. <br/><br/>This is something that showed up in the book. It wasn&apos;t one continuous story where the breaks could be smushed into one book. It was multiple books, with just a continuous character. Because of this shortness character development and plot were really lacking. I was looking for something like <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/search/search?q=I%20am%20Morgan%20LeFay' title='I am Morgan LeFay' rel='nofollow noopener'>I am Morgan LeFay</a> or a R</span>
