<div id="review_14842797" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/14842797" />
    <a title="Kirsten" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/821868-kirsten"><img alt="Kirsten" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1205553862p2/821868.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/14842797?book_show_action=true">Feb 07, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kirsten" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kirsten" href="/user/show/821868-kirsten">Kirsten</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/821868-kirsten?shelf=work-related">work-related</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/821868-kirsten?shelf=own">own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/821868-kirsten?shelf=children-or-ya">children-or-ya</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/821868-kirsten?shelf=read-pre-12-07">read-pre-12-07</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/821868-kirsten?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer14842797" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer63290604620547711">This is really three books in one, but they&apos;re such short YA books that I don&apos;t feel right counting this volume as three. Yolen offers a unique perspective on the Arthurian legend, with this tale of Merlin&apos;s origins. Yolen&apos;s writing is lovely, as usual, but overall this felt kind of slight and I really wished that the book was longer and more in-depth. It ends up feeling more like the taste of a story instead of like three novels.</span>
  <span id="freeText63290604620547711" style="display:none">This is really three books in one, but they're such short YA books that I don't feel right counting this volume as three. Yolen offers a unique perspective on the Arthurian legend, with this tale of Merlin's origins. Yolen's writing is lovely, as usual, but overall this felt kind of slight and I really wished that the book was longer and more in-depth. It ends up feeling more like the taste of a story instead of like three novels.</span>
  <a data-text-id="63290604620547711" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


