        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer600885276" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14416700761761363100">This book is three novels in one, and it took me a while to get into it. I think part of the reason for that is because it depicts the wizard Merlin differently than any portrayals I have ever seen. However, one thing I did like about it was the boy Merlin&apos;s evolution, from eight-year-old child to twelve-year-old child. You could see the changes in him as he matures and comes into himself. However, I don&apos;t know if this is a book I would read again in a hurry. </span>
